Owuor said his heart was clean after talking to Mills and his assistant Collins Gaya during his brief visit to the country last week. Australian coach Liz Mills will handle Kenya Morans in their Fiba Afrobasket Group “C”final round of qualifiers in Yaounde, Cameroon late this month.
Team head coach Cliff Owuor will not be in Cameroon for qualifiers as he his is tied down with club duty at Rwanda Patriotic Army (APR).
Owuor failed to secure release from his new employers APR after joining them last year from United States International University (USIU).



